{"tid":1831093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭成績表：香港連續10年成全球樓價最難負擔城市　為上樓市民要不吃喝逾20年","createTime":"2020-01-20T06:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:39:10.000Z","uid":42246,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b11b182d3cf53cb8cf750356ee36d63ec1d06d9a","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"香港仍然是全球置業負擔最沉重城市。據調查機構Demographia最新發表的調查報告顯示，香港連續10年成為樓價最難負擔城市榜首，樓價對家庭入息中位數，則由上一次調查的20.9倍，略為改善至20.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n調查以截至去年第3季數據，顯示香港樓價中位數為704萬元，而家庭入息中位數為33.8萬元。若家庭息中位數計算，即港人為上樓要不吃不喝20.8年。<br />\n<br />\n報告﹕樓價中位數為704萬元<br />\n<br />\n那麼700萬元左右可以購入一個怎樣的單位。翻查資料顯示，長實集團（1113）去年10月開售位於深水埗項目愛海頌首批單位時，一個面積488平方呎的2房單位，折實售價為721.7萬元。<br />\n<br />\n香港樓價高企與供應不足有相當關係。報告指出，自上世紀70年代，香港政府透過控制土地供應，變相控制了住宅供應；又指出樓價高企與綠化帶等監管環境有關。<br />\n<br />\n為解決香港樓價高企問題，土地供應專責小組於2018年提出填海等方案以增加房屋供應，及減輕市民負擔。在去年個別私人發展商捐出或借出部份農地，以應對房屋供應短缺問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時有85000？ 我屌你老母香港政府</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed2332bc86fadbe4318fdfaec699e33bab2598a4","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十年啦 我屌你老母<br />\n香港政府去食屎啦</span>"},{"pid":"d23f321b465f6b1ae586aca9ebcd8419e955ce4c","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用中位數計<br />\n要不吃不喝20年先買到樓呀<br />\n真係服撚左香港人 到第今年先爆</span>"},{"pid":"ce22adf8fc474667355e32346c6aaffb8e925f77","tid":1831093,"uid":207614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"土地政策、人口政策同炒樓先係問題<br />\n唔好再比佢尻up話冇地冇樓 收皮啦"},{"pid":"6ad7103733aa6ae7b77136d77bc8a39bb8c2718c","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ce22adf8fc474667355e32346c6aaffb8e925f77","tid":1831093,"uid":207614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"土地政策、人口政策同炒樓先係問題<br />\n唔好再比佢尻up話冇地冇樓 收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"當年老野都推到85000<br />\n點會冇地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你整個65000先羅"},{"pid":"60ef5e94b76436a89618d0eca16390d5905f42f2","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cf68c89da0d2431dbbac76ac194566d417b0bd","tid":1831093,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"馬上停止150及各種輸入低端人口政策"},{"pid":"0a39845bbd1400369a823de9426b696aaec6bf36","tid":1831093,"uid":11454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:57:31.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：9成按， 呼吸plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b54bbc05038d53626895183516e4c7be886c3b8","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a7c9d3df8fc62dacff13f21bb3cad73c14dc24","tid":1831093,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53d1113f4e5b82cd06a5984de40b6f2e0ecef59","tid":1831093,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"講得太多，無乜感覺"}]}